    <item>
      <title>韩国严厉打击俄罗斯石油产品搁浅海上</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/russian-oil-product-cargoes-stranded-as-south-korea-cracks-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于韩国买家变得谨慎，来自俄罗斯的石油产品货物在海上堆积如山，凸显出乌克兰入侵事件在两年多后仍然对石油运输产生影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/russian-oil-product-cargoes-stranded-as-south-korea-cracks-down</guid>
